Class ArraySort<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wmich.cs3310.MPeter.hw2.ArraySort<T>

    IArraySort<T>

    public class ArraySort<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IArraySort<T>
    This class is used to sort arrays with a variety of sorting methods, including: Bubble-Sort, Merge-Sort, Quick-Sort, Insertion-Sort, Built-In-Sort, and Selection-Sort.
